# supercronic crontab — runs in container TZ=Europe/London.
#
# NOTE: supercronic reads this file verbatim. Shell-style env expansion
# (${CRON_SCHEDULE}, ${OUTPUT_RETENTION_DAYS}) does NOT happen here.
# Earlier comments suggested those env vars were honored — they were not,
# so the env-knobs are dropped from the compose to stop being misleading.
# To change the schedule or retention, edit THIS file (or render it from
# a template in entrypoint.sh before launching supercronic).
0 3 * * * /app/run-daily.sh
0 4 * * * find /data/output -name "*.json" -type f -mtime +30 -delete
